## parseModule() function

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Parses a TypeScript declaration string into a ModuleAnalysis.

This uses @<!-- -->typescript-eslint/typescript-estree for parsing and produces an AST-based analysis without type resolution. For type resolution, use parseWithTypes().

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function parseModule(source: string, options?: ParseOptions): ModuleAnalysis;
```
